1
00:00:01,602 --> 00:00:02,703
Right.

2
00:00:02,736 --> 00:00:05,605
So even though we got in
a few fights back in town

3
00:00:05,639 --> 00:00:09,409
with both the Franky Family and
with the Galley-La shipwrights,

4
00:00:09,443 --> 00:00:13,446
the enemy we're all going
after here is one and the same.

5
00:00:14,448 --> 00:00:17,017
From this point forward,
we fight as one!

6
00:00:17,050 --> 00:00:19,687
Now Gum-Gum--

7
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:22,122
Three Hundred Caliber--

8
00:00:23,657 --> 00:00:26,393
We're gonna crash!

9
00:00:33,033 --> 00:00:35,903
Cannon!

10
00:00:35,936 --> 00:00:41,041
We... We made it!

11
00:00:44,144 --> 00:00:45,445
That you, Luffy?

12
00:00:45,478 --> 00:00:47,681
Yep, it's me!

13
00:00:47,715 --> 00:00:48,715
What's up?

14
00:00:48,748 --> 00:00:50,450
You save Robin?

15
00:00:50,484 --> 00:00:52,018
No, sorry.

16
00:00:52,052 --> 00:00:53,621
Afraid I'm still
working on that one.

17
00:00:53,654 --> 00:00:57,458
Nami told me why Robin
surrendered and all that stuff.

18
00:00:57,491 --> 00:00:59,059
I see.

19
00:00:59,092 --> 00:01:00,460
That's good.

20
00:01:00,494 --> 00:01:04,231
Well anyway,
you know what's next.

21
00:01:04,264 --> 00:01:06,333
Go ahead give 'em hell, Sanji.

22
00:01:06,366 --> 00:01:08,168
He'll die if he fights them now!

23
00:01:08,202 --> 00:01:11,071
If wants to stand a chance,
he's gotta wait on us!

24
00:01:11,104 --> 00:01:12,672
Hey, Cook, can you hear me?

25
00:01:12,706 --> 00:01:15,709
Some of the guys on that
train are really tough--

26
00:01:15,742 --> 00:01:17,277
Zoro!

27
00:01:17,311 --> 00:01:19,112
It's fine.

28
00:01:20,914 --> 00:01:24,851
If it was you, would you wait?

29
00:01:25,518 --> 00:01:28,255
If you were on that train
right now instead of him and

30
00:01:28,288 --> 00:01:32,426
I told you that Robin sacrificed
herself to protect us.

31
00:01:32,459 --> 00:01:35,295
Would you just sit
there and do nothing?

32
00:01:36,897 --> 00:01:38,933
No use trying to stop him.

33
00:01:38,966 --> 00:01:40,334
But thanks, Moss Head.

34
00:01:40,367 --> 00:01:42,803
I never knew you cared
about me so much.

35
00:01:42,836 --> 00:01:44,238
I hope they kill you!

36
00:01:44,271 --> 00:01:46,173
Anyway, that settles it.

37
00:01:46,207 --> 00:01:50,410
I was willing to fight for Robin
even before I knew the truth.

38
00:01:50,444 --> 00:01:53,881
But now that you told me
how she really feels.

39
00:01:53,914 --> 00:01:57,317
I wouldn't stop,
even if you begged me.

40
00:01:57,351 --> 00:02:02,856
No, I'm... I'm not coming.

41
00:02:02,890 --> 00:02:04,758
Eh?

42
00:02:04,791 --> 00:02:08,028
This doesn't have anything
to do with me anymore.

43
00:02:08,061 --> 00:02:09,964
You're about to make
yourselves personal enemies

44
00:02:09,997 --> 00:02:11,765
of the World Government.

45
00:02:11,798 --> 00:02:13,533
I don't wanna be
any part of that.

46
00:02:13,567 --> 00:02:18,139
Besides, Luffy and the
rest of the crew are coming.

47
00:02:18,172 --> 00:02:22,075
I still feel bad for
Robin but I'm sorry.

48
00:02:22,109 --> 00:02:24,311
It's not my job
to save her anymore.

49
00:02:24,344 --> 00:02:27,180
I am not a part of Luffy's crew!

50
00:02:32,619 --> 00:02:34,221
See ya.

51
00:02:39,126 --> 00:02:41,595
Ahhh! They're right here!

52
00:02:41,628 --> 00:02:42,896
Dammit, they found us!

53
00:02:42,929 --> 00:02:45,165
Metallic Star!

54
00:02:51,839 --> 00:02:54,274
Who the hell are you?!

55
00:03:00,914 --> 00:03:02,916
Your friend told me everything.

56
00:03:02,949 --> 00:03:04,017
I understand that you're here

57
00:03:04,051 --> 00:03:06,320
to rescue a certain
mademoiselle.

58
00:03:06,353 --> 00:03:10,090
That alone is reason enough
for me to join your cause.

59
00:03:10,123 --> 00:03:13,260
My weapons are at your disposal.

60
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:23,603
My name is Sniper King.

61
00:03:44,024 --> 00:03:46,826
♪ Oh, the wind
carries my name. ♪

62
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:50,564
♪ From Sniper Island,
far away. ♪

63
